[SN]TITLE[SN]
Has life improved for women under the African Union?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The African Union (AU) summit is taking place in South Africa, and this year's theme focuses on women's development and empowerment.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
9 June 2015 Last updated at 16:18 BST
But what has changed for women since the AU launched in 2002?
BBC Africa asks what life looks like for today's women on the continent.
Baya Cat reports.
Data source: 2014 African Union report
